<a name="car"></a>
<b>Saturday, January 6</b><p>

<font size="1">SE1 SuperSession: </font><br>
<font class="subhead">The Digital Car Revolution<br></font>
<font class="subhead2">Saturday January 6, 1:30 pm-3:00 pm, Riviera Royale 4</font><p>

The digital evolution of mobile electronics products is having a tremendous impact on both the automotive OEM and 
aftermarket industries. Innovations in IDB, 42-volt, multiplexing, digital wireless connectivity, fiber 
optics and in-car 
digital networking have changed the entire landscape of mobile electronics. New opportunities emerge rapidly for 
manufacturers and retailers to bring the latest electronics to 
consumers, as the OEM design cycle gets shorter and the car's networking infrastructure grows more powerful. 
Discover how the industry is creating new business models, partnerships and delivery channels for its most competitive participants.
