<a name="music"></a>
<b>Sunday, January 7</b><p>

<font size="1">SE5 SuperSession:</font><br> 
<font class="subhead">Surround Music Roundtable<br></font>
<font class="subhead2">Sunday, January 7, 10:00 am-11:30 am, Alexis Park<p></font>

Multichannel surround music is the hottest thing in audio today, but how do studios, producers and recording engineers address sound-quality issues as new approaches are used to 
create a more realistic experience? Leaders in specialty audio and recording engineers discuss this and other 
issues related to multichannel music.<p>

<b><u>Moderator</u>:</b>
 
