Editor-in-Chief<br>
Family PC<a name="outfit2"></a><p> 
</font></td></tr></table>
<p>

<font size="1">SEB SuperSession: </font><br>
<font class="subhead">Outfitting The Digital Consumer-Part Two</font><br>
<font class="subhead2">Sunday, January 7, 12:30 pm-2:00 pm, Room: LVCC N257</font><p>

Digital products abound for the consumer at work, home and play. Join this session for three separate 
discussions that will focus on mobile technologies for work, technologies for play and all the new technologies 
to connect our homes. Hear about the essential trends developing today for the digital consumer.<p>

