<font class="subhead">Home Networking</font><br> 
<font class="subhead2">Monday, January 8, 1:30 pm-3:00 pm, Room: LVCC N257</font><p>

Join consumer electronics and integrated home systems industry experts in a candid exploration of 
the present and future of home networking. Find out what devices can be networked, how they are linked, 
what information they share and what standards are used to make them communicate. Learn what consumers 
